# @COMMENT: This refers to an event apparently late in Muḥammad's life when it became difficult for him to complete the recitation of the prayer. It is also found in the witnesses of WWAAA, WASKA, WISUL, WSACD, WMSAH and WAYA but the list of witnesses is somewhat diferent. The eyewitness to the event is listed as ʿUbādah b. al-Ṣāmit (see BYTXV01P131D).

